Project Bookworm
Written in Node.js

A complete web application that uses a custom RESTful API also written specifically for this application.
Admins can manage book inventory. Users can browse and purchase books through the Paymayo custom payment gateway written in Java.
User can also share the book they want in social media through the in-app Facebook integration.

Node.js module dependencies:
- Consolidate
- Swig
- Mongoose
- OAuth

This application uses MongoDB as the persistence layer.

